{"tid":1693688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啟發post «10月份零售攬炒成績表»","createTime":"2019-11-04T17:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T02:03:53.000Z","uid":286424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7e515c8a309a3eebdbd67ccda081c611a6612732","tid":1693688,"uid":286424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:51:48.000Z","msg":"首先係度講大家咁多個月嘅努力係無白費嘅！特別係10月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係見有好多人話有興趣打經濟戰，於是我用咗幾日時間整合咗尖沙咀、銅鑼灣、沙田三大戰區嘅服裝類零售生意啟發下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 鼓勵類: 對比上年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVWHvA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVWHvA7.png&h=92b005cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P09aA8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P09aA8.png&h=e836d231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 基本上成條線係掂唔到上年，證明今年係跌到仆街<br />\n- 月頭係平均跌50%左右，但後半個月明顯有上升翻，主要係平日嘅下晝多翻支那西購物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 分區生意額: 則係你哋最<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該</span></strong></span>搞嘅地區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SZG01L8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSZG01L8.png&h=c5b24769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 留意下10月1號5號係全線無開，諗下嗰2日我哋有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 見唔見到灰色條bar長期高企呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係尖沙咀呀~ 海港城係香港三大商場之一，廣東道係全球最搵錢嘅零售街道之一，代表d咩自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 時段分析: 平日晏晝真係好好生意㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGX7GOb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGX7GOb.png&h=867c047a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/05/011557_baeefe5c530d30abc577d6abcc8bc529.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F05%2F011557_baeefe5c530d30abc577d6abcc8bc529.png&h=d4e552f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 基本上你睇到8成生意都係集中係5點半，當中黨鐵嘅助攻係非常有效<br />\n- 點解5點前仲咁好生意呢？因為真。香港人都係鐘意遲到嘅，相對地狗隻tg放題都係會4點打後，而趕入商場會係仲5-6點依d時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦屌，講完咁耐則係點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分析得嚟嘅就係如果真係想打商場戰攬炒經濟<br />\n1. 最好嘅方法就係引popo入商場開波，所以舖頭然落閘大吉，重點係愈早愈好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 戰略價值: 香港人成日講性價比所以cost effective係好緊要，排名先後尖沙咀&gt;銅鑼灣&gt;沙田<br />\n<br />\n好處:<br />\n1. 如果有文宣嚇到d商場自動收皮=不戰而勝 (但依家比較難，因為佢知大部分舖頭都唔係中資，都可以做到生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n2. 去到興奮嘅咪<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">講嘢大聲d</span></strong></span>，開心嘅咪唱下歌咁囉，記住你把口就係你嘅樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係唔犯法㗎<br />\n<br />\n3. 假日好多一家大細，最緊要嘅係好多偽中立藍絲係到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果咁啱經過popo話我支持你㗎，點知轉個頭就比人噴胡椒比人話黑記咪扮嘢，個心理陰暗好大㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 藍絲屌人時建議有popo嚟到附近就將佢一秒變黃絲(銀髮族，中佬，師奶屌佢黃屍聽講有+x，順便扮藍絲保安全)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後帶翻個頭盔先:<br />\n以上資料<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>全屬虛構</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，理性分析，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>反對</strong></span></span>暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />建議大家合法去行街<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">eyes</span></strong></span> shopping！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，決一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小小零售銷售分析員上"},{"pid":"485142db52f64fd6078f07ce091a2f186108889e","tid":1693688,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"f4032a3d08a2f2abfe8ae610578a50ced4bad111","tid":1693688,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"28fca68e47a77a84d5ee30d816247356aeb0428e","tid":1693688,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:11:12.000Z","msg":"D數據有無source"},{"pid":"a17ab40b6aee10515108f222cd2d1cb1010ea261","tid":1693688,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:13:53.000Z","msg":"想問問d source邊度拎？ <br />\n我都想睇下成績表分數<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e6a047621ceb29d97987057e1fe72c133153db","tid":1693688,"uid":286424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28fca68e47a77a84d5ee30d816247356aeb0428e","tid":1693688,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:11:12.000Z","msg":"D數據有無source"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:21:27.000Z","msg":"睇嚟大家都好關心d source係邊度嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只可以講係以單一品牌計，但依個品牌/集團絕對代表到中高檔男女裝服飾市場嘅生意流向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係用咗各區兩間舖嚟分析岀嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">留意翻成個post最後嗰句</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a75546c53722d596510891a243c316e6f6d6c4c","tid":1693688,"uid":286424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17ab40b6aee10515108f222cd2d1cb1010ea261","tid":1693688,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:13:53.000Z","msg":"想問問d source邊度拎？ <br />\n我都想睇下成績表分數<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /